               <div class="et_pb_text_inner">
                  <p>Our Services are intended for general audiences and are not intended for individuals under the age of 16. &nbsp;No one under the age of 16 may provide any personal information through the Services, Program, or while otherwise interacting with Power Market. We do not knowingly collect Personal Information from our Services from users in this age group. If we learn that we have collected or received personal information from a child under the age of 16, we will delete that information. If you believe we might have any information from or about a child under 16, please contact us at the email address below.</p>
               </div>
